"We were very excited to have Brandon as our guest speaker. His event was very insightful into one of the most popular â€œbuzz wordsâ€ in modern marketing. Brandon offered a different perspective on the advantagesÂ andÂ disadvantagesÂ of social media and the impact it has on our lives and on business. Our members were able to learn something new about something we all use every day! Brandon did a fantastic job by engage the students and providing very thoughtful answers."

