"As an expert on viral marketing, B.J. Mendelson knows how social media works and for whom it works. But more importantly, he knows why it wonâ€™t work for you. B.J.â€™s candid delivery cut through the bullshit to provide us with the truth about where we should really be putting our marketing dollars. It just adds to his credibility that B.J. wasnâ€™t trying to sell us anything - his discussion was refreshingly void of a sales pitch for his book. This guyâ€™s the real deal!"

