â€œBrandon Mendelsonâ€™s unique history with Twitter made him an ideal speaker for MediaBistroâ€™s first AllTwitter Marketing Conference. Often controversial and frequently polarising, B.J.â€™s session educated attendees on what does and, as often, does not work in social media, and included actionable takeaways on how they can apply these strategies (and avoid the pitfalls) within their own marketing campaigns. Funny and fearless, Brandonâ€™s presentation ignited the show and got the audience â€“ and the event hashtag â€“ buzzing. I look forward to working with him again.â€

