â€œI want to thank Brandon Mendelson for his reasoned, balanced and very professional approach to social media at the recent Westfair Communications debate on social media. It was clear that Brandonâ€™s message resonated with a majority of the audience; many of them made that very clear after the program. He helped present one of the most successful events we have hosted to date.â€

â€”Dee Delbello, Westfair Communications

