â€œI am thankful for the opportunity to have seen Brandonâ€™s presentation at the Associated Collegiate Press convention. Iâ€™ve never encountered a speaker like him, with such a casual and inviting demeanor and a genuine desire to help to [us] students. Brandon was an incredibly compelling, honest speaker with useful and tactful advice for navigating through the world of journalism which, like the rest of the world, is rife with idiots.â€

